title: TV Portal v1.1.4 [Premium] [APK]
description:
Description:
TV Portal indexes free movies and free TV shows and allows you to watch them with minimal hassle on your Android devices. If you think that sounds too good to be true, we give a free 1 week free trial. After your 1 week free trial, TV Shows will be limited to 2 every 5 hours. However, Movies will always be unlimited.

So, try out TV Portal and let us know what you think. What's to lose?



What's New:
-Fixed Mirror Crashing
-Fixed Favs Sort Bug
-Fixed Favs Mirror Blank List
-Fixed thefile.me Force Close



Required Android O/S : 2.3+
